latestPosts.caption:
From red flag to the one - Maiti & Mushand’s love story is 17 years in the making! 💘 What started with friendship (and a little hesitation) led to a Parisian proposal in front of the Eiffel Tower🤩

But let’s be real - Maiti knew all along this was meant to be🫶🏼🥹 Watch their beautiful journey unfold on Nykaa Wali Shaadi, Episode 2, streaming tonight on @officialjiocinema!

#NykaaWaliShaadi #Nykaa

Before the big glam moment comes the big glow moment! ✨

Right before stepping into @makeupbyriddhima’s chair, our Nykaa Wali Bride, Maiti, prepped her skin with the super-nourishing Lancome Advanced Genifique Serum - because nothing says main character energy like radiant, nourished skin! And with its 3D applicator, it’s practically a mini spa moment before the shaadi madness.

Watch her bridal transformation unfold on Nykaa Wali Shaadi, streaming now on @officialjiocinema! 

#NykaaWaliShaadi #Nykaa

For a bride running on zero sleep, a few skipped meals, and peak wedding chaos, Maiti still looked like an absolute dream on her big day! ✨Watch as @makeupbyriddhima works her magic with @kaybykatrina to create the ultimate dreamy, dewy bridal look, because no matter how hectic the shaadi madness gets, the glow must go on!

Catch the full transformation only on @officialjiocinema!

#Nykaa #NykaaWaliShaadi

Maiti and Mushand’s story is equal parts love and equal parts friendship, the perfect formula for lifelong companionship 🥹

Maiti’s bridal nerves could only be calmed because of the love, care and warm hospitality she received from @jwmarriottjuhu in their bridal suite 🤌🏼 

Watch Maiti and Mushand’s #NykaaWaliShaadi only on @officialjiocinema 🫶🏼

#Nykaa

We had the pleasure of collaborating with @mynykaa on a special project, produced by @tigerbabyofficial and directed by @thehouseontheclouds now streaming on @officialjiocinema 

Everyone featured in the episode wore custom Maiti Shahani designs. 

We also had the privilege of attending the Nykaa Waali Shaadi premiere at the Royal Opera House, all dressed in Maiti Shahani.

Luck are those that are blessed with the best girlfriends. 🧿🙌🏼👯‍♀️

Handling decor, to pinning my now husband’s dupatta, to intense pee breaks in what you call a hectic bridal lehenga, to going tie selecting with my baby, to making sure my girlfriends are around, dancing with me & for just being there. 

There is nothing they can’t & won’t do for me. 
I LOVE YOU GIRLS, SO MUCH. 🥹🫂💕😘

My gorgeous girlfriends & I in @maitishahani 

📸 @theweddingvowsofficial 

A few missing but you know who you’ll are. 💕
